# ---- Render outputs --------------------------------------------------------
# Final deliverables go to _output/ via `make ms`, `make supp`, `make ms-supp`,
# `make all`. Track the artefacts so collaborators can grab them without
# rendering; ignore intermediate per-source build artefacts.
